  1→/**
  2→ * Dynamic Behavior Definitions Acceptance Test Kit
  3→ *
  4→ * Extends acceptance-test-kit with helpers specific to the dynamic
  5→ * behavior definition feature set (US-DB-001 through US-DB-004).
  6→ *
  7→ * All helpers use business language -- no technical jargon in function names.
  8→ *
  9→ * Driving ports:
 10→ *   POST /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/behavior-definitions       (definition CRUD)
 11→ *   GET  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/behavior-definitions        (list definitions)
 12→ *   GET  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/behavior-definitions/:id    (definition detail)
 13→ *   PUT  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/behavior-definitions/:id    (update definition)
 14→ *   POST /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/behaviors/score             (telemetry scoring)
 15→ *   GET  /api/workspaces/:workspaceId/behaviors                   (behavior listing)
 16→ *   POST /api/observe/scan/:workspaceId                           (observer graph scan)
 17→ *   SurrealDB direct queries                                      (verification of outcomes)
 18→ */
